Looking at relationship between velocity and the X axis


for (i in 1:length(ind)){
plot(TotalData$v[TotalData$D_V_T==ind[i]],
     TotalData$X[TotalData$D_V_T==ind[i]],
     xlab = "Velocity (cm/s)",
     ylab = "X Axis (cm)",
     main = "") 
}
